(597, 'addiction.png', 'Addiction', 'But if you unplug everything, it gets so quiet you hear that high-pitched empty-room hum.  And then the whispers begin.'),
(598, 'porn.png', 'Porn', 'I have a thing for corrupt women.'),
(599, 'apocalypse.png', 'Apocalypse', 'I wonder if I still have time to go shoot a short film with Kevin Bacon.'),
(600, 'android_boyfriend.png', 'Android Boyfriend', 'Which is, coincidentally, the most unsettling mantlepiece decoration in my house.'),
(601, 'game_theory.png', 'Game Theory', 'Wait, no, that one also loses. How about a nice game of chess?'),
(602, 'overstimulated.png', 'Overstimulated', 'My favorite thing to do at parties is to talk judgementally about people who aren&#39;t there.'),
(603, 'idiocracy.png', 'Idiocracy', 'People aren&#39;t going to change, for better or for worse. Technology&#39;s going to be so cool. All in all, the future will be okay! Except climate; we fucked that one up.'),
