(608, 'form.png', 'Form', '&#39;This space intentionally left blank&#39; is less immediately provocative but more Hofstadterially confusing.'),
(609, 'tab_explosion.png', 'Tab Explosion', 'Cracked.com is another inexplicable browser narcotic.  They could write a list of &#39;17 worst haircuts in the Ottoman Empire&#39; and I&#39;d read through to the end, then click on all the links at the end.'),
