(635, 'locke_and_demosthenes.png', 'Locke and Demosthenes', 'Dear Peter Wiggin: This letter is to inform you that you have received enough upvotes on your reddit comments to become president of the world.  Please be at the UN tomorrow at 8:00 sharp.'),
