(643, 'ohm.png', 'Ohm', 'More generally, with great power comes great dEnergy/dt.'),
(644, 'surgery.png', 'Surgery', 'Damn. Not only did he not install it, he sutured a &#39;Vista-Ready&#39; sticker onto my arm.'),
(645, 'rps.png', 'RPS', 'It looks good, but it needs more postfixins.'),
(646, 'conversations.png', 'Conversations', 'If the dysentery graph looks historically inaccurate it&#39;s because I got all my data from Oregon Trail.'),
(647, 'scary.png', 'Scary', 'I&#39;m teaching every 8-year-old relative to say this, and every 14-year-old to do the same thing with Toy Story.  Also, Pokemon hit the US over a decade ago and kids born after Aladdin came out will turn 18 next year.'),
(648, 'fall_foliage.png', 'Fall Foliage', 'And I could replace you with older pictures of you, from back when you looked happy.'),
(649, 'static.png', 'Static', 'I firmly believe that nothing can go wrong on a project if you&#39;re wearing one of those wrist things.'),
(650, 'nowhere.png', 'Nowhere', 'I mean, seriously, NOWHERE? For starters, there are like a thousand species of dinosaur.'),
(651, 'bag_check.png', 'Bag Check', 'A laptop battery contains roughly the stored energy of a hand grenade, and if shorted it ... hey!  You can&#39;t arrest me if I prove your rules inconsistent!'),
(652, 'more_accurate.png', 'More Accurate', 'We live in a world where there are actual fleets of robot assassins patrolling the skies. At some point there, we left the present and entered the future.'),
(653, 'so_bad_its_worse.png', 'So Bad It&#39;s Worse', 'You think it&#39;s so legendarily bad that you&#39;ll torrent it and sit through it just for the kitschy nerd cred. I, too, once thought as you did.'),
(654, 'nachos.png', 'Nachos', '&#39;Cheater!&#39; &#39;Hey, gaming on wifi? You have only yourself to blame.&#39;'),
(655, 'climbing.png', 'Climbing', 'Where did you even get this wall? Return it there and stand it back up right now.'),
