(665, 'prudence.png', 'Prudence', 'Moments later, the White Witch rolls up and, confused, tries to tempt the probe with a firmware upgrade.'),
(666, 'silent_hammer.png', 'Silent Hammer', 'I bet he&#39;ll keep quiet for a couple weeks and then-- wait, did you nail a piece of scrap wood to my antique table a moment ago?'),
