(668, 'pandora.png', 'Pandora', 'What?  Oh, no, the &#39;Enchanted&#39; soundtrack was just playing because Pandora&#39;s algorithms are terrible.  [silence] ... (quietly) That&#39;s how you knooooooow ...'),
