(689, 'first_design.png', 'FIRST Design', 'Pool on the roof must&#39;ve sprung a leak.'),
(690, 'semicontrolled_demolition.png', 'Semicontrolled Demolition', 'I believe the truth always lies halfway between the most extreme claims.'),
