(692, 'dirty_harry.png', 'Dirty Harry', 'Sci-fi has energy weapons because otherwise the people like me who watch it get distracted counting shots.'),
(693, 'childrens_fantasy.png', 'Children&#39;s Fantasy', 'I was going to be a scientist, but that seems silly now. Magical worlds exist. I&#39;ve learned a huge truth about our place in the universe. I&#39;m supposed to care about college? I mean, FUCK.'),
(694, 'retro_virus.png', 'Retro Virus', 'He says this is the year of Linux on the desktop! The world of Windows will fade any moment now!'),
(695, 'spirit.png', 'Spirit', 'On January 26th, 2274 Mars days into the mission, NASA declared Spirit a &#39;stationary research station&#39;, expected to stay operational for several more months until the dust buildup on its solar panels forces a final shutdown.'),
(696, 'strip_games.png', 'Strip Games', 'HOW ABOUT A NICE GAME OF STRIP GLOBAL THERMONUCLEAR WAR?'),
(697, 'tensile_vs_shear_strength.png', 'Tensile vs. Shear Strength', 'Although really, the damage was done when the party planners took the hole punch to the elevator ribbon to hang up the sign.'),
