(960, 'subliminal.png', 'Subliminal', 'Once you see it, you can&#39;t help seeing it every time. Until your body finishes metabolizing the mushrooms.'),
(961, 'eternal_flame.gif', 'Eternal Flame', 'There&#39;s always the hope that if you sit and watch for long enough, the beachball will vanish and the thing it interrupted will return.'),
